<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 22:08:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>犹太定居者袭击西岸村庄；巴勒斯坦人死亡，一人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-vows-to-prosecute-israeli-settlers-after-deadly-riots-in-west-bank-village/00000191-57a6-dacb-a7bf-f7ae83f10000</link><description>周四晚上，数十名犹太定居者突然袭击吉特，造成至少一人死亡；亚伊尔·戈兰：“定居者是一个暴力团体，得到政府的大力支持”</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 20:38:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-vows-to-prosecute-israeli-settlers-after-deadly-riots-in-west-bank-village/00000191-57a6-dacb-a7bf-f7ae83f10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列退休警察：10月7日是“最基本的失败”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/retired-israeli-cop-only-900-officers-sent-to-south-during-october-7-attack/00000191-573c-d203-abb5-5f3cd1830000</link><description>退役少将阿姆农·阿尔卡莱 (Amnon Alkalay) 表示，“这是一次非常严重、灾难性的管理事件”，他援引了仅向南部派遣 900 名警察的决定，而“人们却连续几个小时遭到屠杀”</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 19:47:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/retired-israeli-cop-only-900-officers-sent-to-south-during-october-7-attack/00000191-573c-d203-abb5-5f3cd1830000</guid></item><item><title>抗议者走上特拉维夫街头，呼吁在卡塔尔峰会期间达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/protesters-take-to-streets-of-tel-aviv-call-for-hostage-deal-amid-qatar-summit/00000191-5713-d79a-a3f5-dfd30adc0000</link><description>一名人质亲属表示，“人质事件是以色列国历史上最大的安全、社会、道德和宗教失败的证据”，示威者敦促以色列谈判代表不要在没有达成协议的情况下从卡塔尔返回</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 19:06:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/protesters-take-to-streets-of-tel-aviv-call-for-hostage-deal-amid-qatar-summit/00000191-5713-d79a-a3f5-dfd30adc0000</guid></item><item><title>中东局势岌岌可危，除了与伊朗全面战争之外，以色列左翼还有其他选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/on-the-israeli-left-there-is-still-an-alternative-to-all-out-war-with-iran/00000191-562b-d61e-a7b1-f7ff54d10000</link><description>左翼在安全问题上始终处于守势。但现在，在等待伊朗袭击以色列的漫长而可怕的等待中，除了内塔尼亚胡的灾难性政策之外，还有一个替代方案：对一个全副武装的誓言敌人采取自由、进步的态度，并有充分的理由进行报复</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 18:50:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/on-the-israeli-left-there-is-still-an-alternative-to-all-out-war-with-iran/00000191-562b-d61e-a7b1-f7ff54d10000</guid></item><item><title>《早安乔》透露：内塔尼亚胡终于失去了亲以色列的美国人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-15/ty-article/.highlight/at-long-last-netanyahu-is-losing-pro-israel-americans/00000191-5674-d887-adbd-77f509d30000</link><description>乔·斯卡伯勒和退役美国海军上将詹姆斯·斯塔夫里迪斯在“早安乔”节目中的对话反映了许多美国人都知道的事情：内塔尼亚胡是一位腐败的政客，不惜一切代价紧握权力</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 18:16:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-15/ty-article/.highlight/at-long-last-netanyahu-is-losing-pro-israel-americans/00000191-5674-d887-adbd-77f509d30000</guid></item><item><title>斯塔默总理当选后，以色列罕见延长驻英国大使任期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/in-rare-move-israel-to-extend-term-of-ambassador-to-u-k-following-election-of-pm-starmer/00000191-56d2-d79a-a3f5-ded20fd30000</link><description>以色列外交部正在寻求延长齐皮·霍托夫利 (Tzipi Hotovley) 以色列驻英国大使的任期，理由是她拥有“广泛的关系网络”以及推进以色列“战略利益”的能力</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 16:52:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/in-rare-move-israel-to-extend-term-of-ambassador-to-u-k-following-election-of-pm-starmer/00000191-56d2-d79a-a3f5-ded20fd30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 314 天：哈马斯称自战争开始以来至少有 40,000 名加沙人被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-314-at-least-40-000-gazans-killed-since-war-began-hamas-says/00000191-5687-d623-a1f3-76d7bdf70000</link><description>以色列代表团抵达卡塔尔，与哈马斯就停火/人质释放协议进行谈判 ■ 白宫：情报显示“伊朗尚未放弃攻击以色列的威胁” ■ 据报道，拜登的中东高级特使表示“需要做什么”黎巴嫩将缓和以色列和真主党之间的紧张局势，并“不破坏调解人为确保停战所做的努力” ■ 这是战争开始 314 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 16:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-314-at-least-40-000-gazans-killed-since-war-began-hamas-says/00000191-5687-d623-a1f3-76d7bdf70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前首席拉比批评本格维尔访问圣殿山</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-former-chief-rabbi-criticizes-ben-gvirs-temple-mount-visit/00000191-5699-db91-a7dd-779981600000</link><description>约瑟夫拉比说：“我们都相信一位上帝，希望各国之间实现和平，我们不能让极端的边缘人士引导我们。”其他主要拉比也谴责周一的访问。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 16:18:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-former-chief-rabbi-criticizes-ben-gvirs-temple-mount-visit/00000191-5699-db91-a7dd-779981600000</guid></item><item><title>白宫表示多哈峰会已经开始，会谈将持续到周五</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/white-house-says-doha-summit-has-started-talks-to-continue-into-friday/00000191-56c1-d79a-a3f5-ded373250000</link><description>以色列和哈马斯周四在卡塔尔重启停火和释放人质协议的谈判</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 16:07:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/white-house-says-doha-summit-has-started-talks-to-continue-into-friday/00000191-56c1-d79a-a3f5-ded373250000</guid></item><item><title>40,000 个关于已不复存在的加沙的提醒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/40-000-reasons-for-thought-testimony-to-the-lives-in-gaza-that-are-no-more/00000191-5656-d623-a1f3-76d781790000</link><description>这里的每个点都象征着一个人、他们的希望和对生活的渴望——尽管如此。加沙战争使他们变得匿名，每个人都只剩下另一个数字</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 15:11:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/40-000-reasons-for-thought-testimony-to-the-lives-in-gaza-that-are-no-more/00000191-5656-d623-a1f3-76d781790000</guid></item><item><title>以色列希望捕获伊朗的“幽灵舰队”，这些油轮在雷达下为其轴心提供资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-wants-to-trap-irans-ghost-fleet-oil-tankers-financing-its-axis-under-the-radar/00000191-5669-d61e-a7b1-f7ff52800000</link><description>《国土报》调查发现，伊朗油轮由世界各地的稻草公司注册，并关闭应答器以隐藏其运营</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 15:04:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-wants-to-trap-irans-ghost-fleet-oil-tankers-financing-its-axis-under-the-radar/00000191-5669-d61e-a7b1-f7ff52800000</guid></item><item><title>袭击以色列高级官员的伊朗黑客现在将目标瞄准特朗普和哈里斯竞选团队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/iranian-hackers-that-hit-top-israelis-officials-now-targeting-trump-harris-campaigns/00000191-55ba-d2c7-a9bf-7dbb8eaa0000</link><description>在特朗普竞选团队确认罗杰·斯通的电子邮件帐户可能遭到黑客攻击后，谷歌研究人员表示，专门针对以色列备受瞩目的政治和安全目标进行网络间谍活动的伊朗组织也瞄准了美国总统竞选活动</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 14:27:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/iranian-hackers-that-hit-top-israelis-officials-now-targeting-trump-harris-campaigns/00000191-55ba-d2c7-a9bf-7dbb8eaa0000</guid></item><item><title>“记住我们的名字”：由于害怕被遗忘，年轻的加沙人在临终前记录了最后的遗嘱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/remember-our-names-fearing-oblivion-young-gazans-recorded-last-wills-before-dying/00000191-4b2b-dfee-a3f3-5feb9a300000</link><description>一位从未离开家的足球运动员、一位想要提高政治意识的经济学家以及一位即使在死后仍继续提供内容的电影制片人。自战争开始以来，他们是加沙地带 4 万人遇难的人之一。除了死亡之外，许多人还担心自己会成为“一个数字”，并采取措施确保他们不会被遗忘</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 13:47:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/remember-our-names-fearing-oblivion-young-gazans-recorded-last-wills-before-dying/00000191-4b2b-dfee-a3f3-5feb9a300000</guid></item><item><title>由辛贝特和摩萨德领导人率领的以色列团队抵达多哈参加加沙停火峰会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/led-by-shin-bet-and-mossad-chiefs-israeli-team-heads-to-doha-for-gaza-cease-fire-summit/00000191-5231-d984-a5ff-f2f713580000</link><description>一名巴勒斯坦高级官员告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡和某些内阁成员的言论表明谈判不太可能取得进展，其成功取决于美国的压力</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 12:29:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/led-by-shin-bet-and-mossad-chiefs-israeli-team-heads-to-doha-for-gaza-cease-fire-summit/00000191-5231-d984-a5ff-f2f713580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列航空公司在加沙战争的帮助下季度利润创纪录的 1.47 亿美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airline-el-al-rakes-in-record-147m-in-quarterly-profits-with-help-of-gaza-war/00000191-552a-d5d7-adbb-757a65c80000</link><description>得益于在以色列运营的外国航空公司的竞争减少，该公司在本世纪初面临着严重的财务困境，但今年第二季度自 2022 年底以来的净财务债务减少了 10.89 亿美元</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airline-el-al-rakes-in-record-147m-in-quarterly-profits-with-help-of-gaza-war/00000191-552a-d5d7-adbb-757a65c80000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯卫生部称，自战争开始以来，加沙死亡人数已超过4万</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/gaza-death-toll-surpasses-40-000-since-war-began-hamas-health-ministry-says/00000191-4c06-d695-a7b5-de0f450a0000</link><description>据哈马斯管理的卫生部称，约 70% 的伤亡者是妇女和儿童，约 17,000 名儿童失去了父母之一或双亲。 ■ 加沙的卫生系统处于崩溃边缘，约 12,000 名伤者需要紧急疏散接受治疗国外</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:08:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/gaza-death-toll-surpasses-40-000-since-war-began-hamas-health-ministry-says/00000191-4c06-d695-a7b5-de0f450a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡办公室要求甘茨偿还美国正式访问费用19,000美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-demands-gantz-pay-back-19-000-for-official-u-s-visit/00000191-54d4-d5d7-adbb-74f406340000</link><description>以色列议员本尼·甘茨（Benny Gantz）还是内塔尼亚胡战时内阁成员时进行的三月访问包括与副总统哈里斯和其他官员的会面。项目办称甘茨无权进行此次访问</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 07:40:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-demands-gantz-pay-back-19-000-for-official-u-s-visit/00000191-54d4-d5d7-adbb-74f406340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列掌握着释放人质的关键 - 但伊朗将决定中东是否爆发战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-holds-the-key-to-freeing-the-hostages-but-iran-decides-if-the-region-goes-to-war/00000191-52b5-dc60-a397-57f5b6310000</link><description>周四的多哈峰会就像一个俄罗斯娃娃，充满了层层障碍：目前还不清楚内塔尼亚胡给了以色列谈判代表多大的灵活性，以及​​这对哈马斯来说是否足够；没有人知道伊朗和真主党是否会以加沙停火为借口，放弃对两起耻辱性暗杀事件的军事反应</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 03:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-holds-the-key-to-freeing-the-hostages-but-iran-decides-if-the-region-goes-to-war/00000191-52b5-dc60-a397-57f5b6310000</guid></item><item><title>美国在加沙峰会前加大压力 - 并计划在失败后改变策略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/u-s-steps-up-the-pressure-ahead-of-gaza-summit-and-plans-a-change-of-tactics-if-it-fails/00000191-521f-dc13-ab99-db1f4aa10000</link><description>拜登政府可能会向以色列和哈马斯提出一个不可谈判的、是或否的主张。如果内塔尼亚胡拒绝，华盛顿可能会将失败归咎于他，并可能对其政府内的极右翼采取进一步行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 03:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/u-s-steps-up-the-pressure-ahead-of-gaza-summit-and-plans-a-change-of-tactics-if-it-fails/00000191-521f-dc13-ab99-db1f4aa10000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和以色列高层政治人物谴责西方银行事件；陆军、辛贝特展开调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article-live/senior-palestinian-official-israeli-comments-suggest-doha-talks-unlikely-to-end-in-deal/00000191-53ce-d6a2-a7dd-d3dea0fb0000</link><description>安全来源：蒙面定居者在西岸放火焚烧建筑物、车辆；红新月会：定居者开火造成一人重伤 ■ 以色列代表团抵达卡塔尔进行停火、释放人质谈判 ■ 数百人聚集在特拉维夫，呼吁达成协议释放人质 ■ 法国、英国外长将于周五在耶路撒冷会见以色列外长■ 黎巴嫩火箭弹袭击以色列北部起火</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 02:26:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article-live/senior-palestinian-official-israeli-comments-suggest-doha-talks-unlikely-to-end-in-deal/00000191-53ce-d6a2-a7dd-d3dea0fb0000</guid></item></channel></rss>